snippet.title: [Steam,Playism]TorqueL (Updated March, 9th)
snippet.description:
TorqueL is a unique 2D "rolling" & "extend" platformer/action/puzzle game.
Including total 50 chambers, 7 basic routes, and 1 secret route.

Interactive music of product version composed by sanodg(Nobuyoshi Sano).

Coming in January, 22 2015 19:00 (PST)

Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/250070
Playism: http://www.playism-games.com/games/torquel/

http://TorqueL.net
